### =============================================
### PUBLIC MERCHANDISE BROWSING (No Authentication)
### =============================================

### Get All In-Stock Merchandise
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/merchandise
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Merchandise with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/merchandise?page=1&per_page=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Merchandise (Including Out of Stock)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/merchandise?in_stock=false
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Specific Merchandise Item
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/merchandise/1
Content-Type: application/json

